IMPOSED AND STAYED SENTENCE OF:   

4 YEARS IMPRISONMENT (CREDIT - 1 days)
  -  2 YEAR(S) OF INITIAL CONFINEMENT
  -  2 YEAR(S) OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION;

TERM OF PROBATION:  2 YEAR(S);

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:  
*AODA Assessment and follow through with any treatment recommended; continue treatment currently involved in.
*D/L Revocation: 36 months;
*IGNITION INTERLOCK: 36 months; The Court grants the IID exemption on the 2006 Harley;

FINE:  $4,563.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $250.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

BLOOD DRAW FEE: $13.14 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

ATTEND Victim Impact Panel (attended 8/20/14);

CONDITION TIME: 9 months, non-working hours, release for treatment and employment.  

IF REVOKED:
Defendant is eligible for Challenge Incarceration Program.
Defendant is eligible for Substance Abuse Program.

Felony warnings, voting rights and firearms warnings given.
